<headline>Special Weather Statement issued December 25 at 12:59PM EST  by NWS New York City - Upton</headline>
<description>Periods of light rain will continue early this afternoon. While
most of the area will have temperatures above freezing. Some spots
may still be freezing, particularly along the Connecticut River
Valley. This may create slippery conditions on untreated
surfaces. Use extra caution if traveling this afternoon.</description>
